              <p class="mb-0 font-weight-bold">Điện thoai</p>
              <p class="mb-4"><a href="#">02413713450</a></p>

              <p class="mb-0 font-weight-bold">Địa chỉ email</p>
              <p class="mb-0"><a href="#">khachsanbkhust@gmail.com</a></p>

